  <summary date="2022-08-17T15:01:38Z" status="Introduced in House">Alzheimer's Accountability and Investment Act

This bill requires the National Institutes of Health to annually submit, beginning in FY2024, an estimate of its budget and personnel needs for carrying out initiatives pursuant to the National Alzheimer's Project. This project supports coordination of federal planning, research, and other efforts to address Alzheimer's disease and related dementias.</summary>
